<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="tr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>TenteCRM - Sizin İçin Tasarlandı</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://unpkg.com/aos@2.3.1/dist/aos.css">
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
            background: #f9f9f9;
            color: #333;
        }

        .hero {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0088cc, #00b894);
            color: white;
            padding: 100px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

            .hero h1 {
                font-size: 48px;
                margin-bottom: 20px;
            }

            .hero p {
                font-size: 20px;
                margin-bottom: 30px;
            }

            .hero .cta-buttons button {
                background: white;
                color: #00a8ff;
                border: none;
                padding: 15px 25px;
                margin: 10px;
                font-size: 16px;
                border-radius: 10px;
                cursor: pointer;
                transition: all 0.3s ease;
            }

                .hero .cta-buttons button:hover {
                    background: #f0f0f0;
                }

        .section {
            padding: 80px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

            .section h2 {
                font-size: 36px;
                margin-bottom: 30px;
            }

        .feature-grid {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 30px;
        }

        .feature {
            background: white;
            padding: 30px;
            width: 250px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }

            .feature i {
                font-size: 36px;
                color: #00b894;
                margin-bottom: 15px;
            }

        .whatsapp-button {
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 30px;
            right: 30px;
            z-index: 100;
        }

            .whatsapp-button a {
                background: #25D366;
                color: white;
                padding: 15px 20px;
                border-radius: 50px;
                text-decoration: none;
                font-size: 18px;
                box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
            }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <!-- Hero Bölümü -->
    <section class="hero" data-aos="fade-up">
        <h1>Bayilerinize Özel Teklifler Sunmanın En Kolay Yolu!</h1>
        <p>Dinamik hesaplama tabloları, yetkilendirme sistemi ve daha fazlası TenteCRM ile</p>
        <div class="cta-buttons">
            <button onclick="window.location.href='/Login'">Ücretsiz Dene</button>
            <button onclick="window.open('https://wa.me/905555555555','_blank')">WhatsApp ile Sor</button>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Özellikler Bölümü -->
    <section class="section" data-aos="fade-up">
        <h2>Öne Çıkan Özellikler</h2>
        <div class="feature-grid">
            <div class="feature" data-aos="zoom-in">
                <i class="fas fa-calculator"></i>
                <h4>Formül Hesaplama</h4>
                <p>Bayiler kendi verilerini girerek anında fiyat hesaplayabilir.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature" data-aos="zoom-in" data-aos-delay="100">
                <i class="fas fa-user-lock"></i>
                <h4>Yetki Yönetimi</h4>
                <p>Her bayiye özel erişim, görünürlük ve işlem izinleri.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature" data-aos="zoom-in" data-aos-delay="200">
                <i class="fas fa-mobile-alt"></i>
                <h4>Mobil Uyumlu</h4>
                <p>Mobilde, tablette ve her cihazda sorunsuz deneyim.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature" data-aos="zoom-in" data-aos-delay="300">
                <i class="fas fa-cloud"></i>
                <h4>Bulut Altyapı</h4>
                <p>Verileriniz güvenli ve erişilebilir şekilde saklanır.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- WhatsApp Canlı Destek Butonu -->
    <div class="whatsapp-button">
        <a href="https://wa.me/905555555555" target="_blank">
            <i class="fab fa-whatsapp"></i> Canlı Destek
        </a>
    </div>

    <script src="https://unpkg.com/aos@2.3.1/dist/aos.js"></script>
    <script>
        AOS.init();
    </script>
</body>
</html>
